{"decisions": [{"obligation_id": "EUAIA-OBL-008", "decision": "flag_for_review", "reasoning": "GOVERN-1.1 at 0.85 is a solid anchor mapping — the obligation is fundamentally a legal prohibition whose operationalisation requires understanding, managing, and documenting the regulatory requirement. That call is defensible and requires no further scrutiny.

